{
  "stem": "2118.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we marched all day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We made maybe 25 kilometers or 20 miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And then we-- they-- they-- we came to a little town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But there was the [INAUDIBLE]-- the [INAUDIBLE]-- the pencils, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They-- the whole town worked for [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The whole town-- it was a little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after maybe five days march or something, they took us back to Sonneberg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, there's no place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the Americans, we get surrounded and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't to march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, the SS didn't want really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they had enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came back into our camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we found out that in the meantime, another group of marchers stayed over in our camp a couple days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they marched them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They don't want people-- so we marched again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Buchenwald, was the same story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- they had to march too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we marched for four weeks, maybe five, from the end of March to the 9th-- to the 9th of May.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to-- we went down to Czechoslovakia toward what they called Sudetendeutschland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the way we marched, we got weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Food was given to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then some SS man went ahead, and they get the farmers to get some food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So if we got a couple potatoes, which was cooked in those big-- we used to call them pig-- pig-- it was a big pot, you know, where they cooked for the-- for the-- for the pigs.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like a boiler-- as big as a water boiler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you got a potato too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was-- was-- that was about the size of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we came to one place one time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we each we get a free potato or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
